        "Instructions": "['Preheat oven to 425°. Toss vegetables with oil on a rimmed baking sheet to coat; season with salt and pepper. Roast until deep golden brown and tender, 20–25 minutes. Let cool slightly, then toss with nutritional yeast.', 'Do Ahead: Veggies can be made 5 days ahead. Cover and chill.']",
