        "Ingredients": "[' 4 large ripe (but not too ripe) yellow peaches, sliced ', ' 1 cup blackberries ', ' ¾ cup blueberries ', ' Seeds from 1 medium pomegranate ', ' 6 large basil leaves, cut into ribbons ', ' 1-2 teaspoons honey ', ' ½ lime, juiced ']",
